Record Class UnbakedCTLayer

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
com.kneelawk.kmodlib.client.blockmodel.ct.UnbakedCTLayer
Record Components:
exteriorCorners - exterior corner sprite supplier.
interiorCorners - interior corner sprite supplier.
horizontalEdges - horizontal edges sprite supplier.
verticalEdges - vertical edges sprite supplier.
noEdges - no edges sprite supplier.
material - material to render with.
depth - depth to render at.
cullFaces - whether to cull faces.
interiorBorder - whether to have borders inside a corner between three blocks in an L shape.
tintIndex - tint index to render with.
connector - the connector to control which blocks to connect to.
